reviewText:
Zombies on a Plane is an exciting new survival game.
The action take place in the sky where you can to take on the role of the captain of a troubled jumbo jet or  loner hero.
In the shooting mode you can choose options: on the outside, in a cabine and to hold out against horde.
Shooting mode in a cabine very difficult because picture and animation is fuzzy, some zombi  move only crawl and  you don't see they.
In the  flying mode you can choose several  options of flying too, but
I didn't feel any different.

Pros:
- original idea;
- outdoor graphics;
- achievements;
- trading cards;
- mod options;
- funny skins;
- language support.

Cons:
- graphic design;
- zombie animation;
- bad controls;
- similar background  landscape;
- game breaking bugs.

In summary, Zombies on a Plane have potenshial but need  improvement.
